filename-lint.invalid-file-name: File name does not match the format: {0}
filename-lint.invalid-dir-name: Directory name does not match the format: {0}
filename-lint.presetPattern:
Select a preset naming format specification.
lowercase: /^[^A-Z]+$/
kebab-case: /^[a-z0-9]+(-[a-z0-9]+)*$/
snake_case: /^[a-z0-9]+(_[a-z0-9]+)*$/
camelCase: /^[a-z0-9]+[a-z0-9]*([A-Z][a-z0-9]*)*$/
PascalCase: /^[A-Z]+[a-z0-9]*([A-Z0-9][a-z0-9]*)*$/
custom: custom regex expression by filename-lint.customRegex
filename-lint.customRegex: Custom regular expression. (effective when presetPatterns is custom)
filename-lint.ignorePatterns:
Ignore file patterns. (glob syntax)
 Default Value: ["**/node_modules/**","**/.git/**","**/.idea/**"]
